snippet.title: Barron Trump Singing on America's Got Talent Imagined--America Needs God
snippet.description:
America Needs God

⬇️⬇️⬇️ Watch more videos below! ⬇️⬇️⬇️
https://youtu.be/WBHJZs8ZeFQ
https://youtu.be/GAdihLnAiXk
https://youtu.be/SZZW8YMZlMg?si=kP7ZE5s5fhhjjpX2
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hq_JjAodbY0

Lyrics:
I see the struggle, I hear the cries,
A nation lost beneath the skies.
We're chasing riches, we’re chasing fame,
But we’ve forgotten His holy name.

Chorus:
America needs God, now more than ever,
A light to guide us through stormy weather.
He is the answer, He is the way,
Only through Him can we be saved.

Verse 2:
We've built the towers, we’ve made the plans,
But turned away from His guiding hands.
Through every trial, through every test,
Only with faith can we be blessed.

Chorus:
America needs God, now more than ever,
A light to guide us through stormy weather.
He is the answer, He is the way,
Only through Him can we be saved.

Bridge:
Turn back now, lift your eyes,
Grace is waiting, hope won’t die.
If we kneel, if we pray,
God will lead us back His way.

Final Chorus:
America needs God, let’s stand as one,
With faith and truth, His will be done.
A nation strong, a people free,
Only through God can we believe.

Outro:
Let the church bells ring, let the people sing,
America needs God in everything.
If we turn to Him, if we hold on,
Our land will rise, our faith be strong.
